gdlex-ocr (0.1.3) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add an auditable manifest.json for OCR and conversion jobs.
  * Verify generated outputs against the manifest.
  * Add actions to open the manifest and log and to verify outputs.
  * Centralize standard output paths in output_layout.py.
  * Add offline tests for manifests, output layout, GUI actions, and Debian payload.

